<div class="container">
  <h1>🍪 Cookie Policy</h1>
  <div class="subhead">Last updated: 13 July 2026 · Rheoa RPG</div>

  <p>
    Rheoa RPG (“we”, “us”, or “our”) uses cookies and similar tracking technologies 
    to enhance your experience, remember your preferences, and understand how you 
    interact with our game. This policy explains what cookies are, why we use them, 
    and how you can manage them – because your privacy matters, no matter where you 
    are in the world.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet, 
    or mobile) when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work 
    more efficiently, to remember your choices, and to provide information to the 
    site owners.
  </p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 22%;">Type</th>
        <th style="width: 48%;">Purpose</th>
        <th style="width: 30%;">Examples</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="badge">Strictly Necessary</span></td>
        <td>Essential for the game to function – authentication, security, and load balancing.</td>
        <td>Supabase session tokens, auth state.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="badge">Functional / Preferences</span></td>
        <td>Remember your choices so we can personalise your experience.</td>
        <td>Theme (Aurora/Dusk/Meadow), font preference, active language.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="badge">Analytics / Performance</span></td>
        <td>Help us understand how you use Rheoa, so we can improve performance and fix issues.</td>
        <td>Page views, total visits, device information (browser, OS).</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="badge">Third-Party / Affiliate</span></td>
        <td>Enable external services and track affiliate referrals (e.g., Hot Wheels collectibles).</td>
        <td>ipinfo.io (geolocation), affiliate link clicks, Google OAuth.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <strong>⚡ Important:</strong> We do <em>not</em> sell your personal data, and we
    never use cookies to track you across unrelated websites. All analytics are 
    anonymised where possible.
  </div>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    Some features on Rheoa rely on trusted third‑party services. These providers may 
    place their own cookies on your device:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Supabase</strong> – our backend platform, uses session cookies for authentication and real‑time updates.</li>
    <li><strong>ipinfo.io</strong> – used to approximate your location for regional game features and analytics. No personal data is stored.</li>
    <li><strong>Google OAuth</strong> – if you log in via Google, Google’s authentication cookies are used (see Google’s Privacy Policy).</li>
    <li><strong>Affiliate links</strong> – when you click “Collect Now” on Hot Wheels products, the affiliate network may place a cookie to track referrals for commissions (at no extra cost to you).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Your Choices & Consent</h2>
  <p>
    When you first visit Rheoa, you will see a cookie banner. By clicking <strong>“Accept”</strong>, 
    you consent to the use of all cookies described in this policy. If you choose 
    not to accept, we will only set strictly necessary cookies.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can also:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time by clearing your browser’s cookies and local storage, or by changing your browser settings.</li>
    <li><strong>Control cookies</strong> through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to block or delete cookies entirely. Check your browser’s “Help” section for instructions.</li>
    <li><strong>Disable third‑party tracking</strong> via browser extensions (e.g., Privacy Badger, uBlock Origin).</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <strong>🌍 Global Compliance:</strong> Rheoa is designed to respect your privacy
    rights under the <strong>GDPR</strong> (EU/UK), <strong>CCPA/CPRA</strong> (California),
    and other international privacy frameworks. We do not process your data without
    a lawful basis, and we limit data retention to what is necessary.
  </div>

  <h2>5. Data Security & Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We treat your data with the same care we would want for ourselves. Cookies that 
    contain personal identifiers (like your user ID) are encrypted and stored securely. 
    Most preference cookies (theme, font) are retained for up to <strong>12 months</strong> 
    from your last visit, after which they may be automatically cleared.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, your privacy, or how we 
    handle your data, please reach out to us:
  </p>
  <ul style="list-style-type: '📧 ';">
    <li>Email: <strong>support@rheoa.com</strong></li>
    <li>In‑game: use the <strong>Secret Admin Panel</strong> (Founder tier) or contact a Moderator in the chat.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    We may update this policy from time to time. Any significant changes will be 
    communicated via the in‑game notification system or by updating the “Last updated” 
    date above.
  </p>

